## Educational Use

This project is developed as part of the HIT137 Software Development course assignment. 
It is intended for educational purposes and demonstrates:

- Object-Oriented Programming principles
- GUI development with Tkinter
- AI model integration using Hugging Face Transformers
- Software engineering best practices

Students and educators are encouraged to use this code for learning purposes 
while respecting academic integrity policies of their respective institutions.

